//Seventh Boo-Wilson Friendship Dialogue — Contentment (while the party is resting)
@68 /*Boo*/ = ~Squeak squeak squeak. *Boo is sprawled on top of Wilson's head, looking a bit excited.*~ [AMB_E45B]
@69 /*Wilson*/ = ~Grumble grumble. *Wilson seems completely unconcerned about the little creature on his head.*~ [OH87188]
@70 /*Boo*/ = ~*Boo's little paws rest gently on Wilson's fur, his tail trembling slightly* Squeak squeak squeak.~
@71 /*Wilson*/ = ~*Wilson's eyes are half-closed, as if he's asleep, but he's still responding to Boo* Arooo.~
@72 /*Boo*/ = ~*Boo spins in two circles on top of Wilson's head, as if searching for a nest to sleep in* Coo coo.~
@73 /*Wilson*/ = ~*Wilson's ears twitch gently, allowing the little creature to spin around on his head* Grumble grumble.~
