@77 /*Minsc*/ = ~*Sleep-talking* Boo... Wilson... Minsc... best companions... together... go home...~
@78 /*Wilson*/ = ~*Wilson is utterly indifferent to the little fellow plucking his fur on top of his head, letting out a long sigh.* Hmph...~